folder: West End Avenue & 63rd Street (West), Manhattan, NY
text:
West End Avenue, west side, at W.63rd Street. The views are southwestward across the New York Central Railroad yards toward the Hudson River and the grain elevator of the railroad company.
View 2 shows the new West Side Express Vehicular Highway.

P.L.Sperr

View1: March 19, 1930
View 2: December 19, 1937
